data.description: 2 LOTS for the price of one! Low assumable rate! The ideal situation for a qualified buyer! This 4-bed, 2-bath home with a 2-car garage is a haven of comfort. Situated on over 1+ acres with the ability to subdivide and build another home or enjoy a massive piece of land in a great neighborhood. There is limitless potential to have your very own backyard oasis or second home to use as a rental. Take advantage of the 30-year rebate on the solar and enjoy little to no electric bills! Upon entering you're greeted with vaulted ceilings and 3 skylights that bring in tons of natural light into the space. The kitchen is a chef's delight with a breakfast bar and granite countertops, combining style and practicality. The living room is expansive, featuring a beautiful stone fireplace for cozy evenings and gatherings. Indulge in the plush carpeting found in all bedrooms, including the master. The ensuite is a retreat with a jetted garden tub, a separate shower, and dual vanity sinks, creating a spa-like atmosphere. Whether you're enjoying the spacious interior or the expansive backyard, this home offers a lifestyle of comfort and relaxation. Home has a VA loan at a very low-interest rate that may be assumed by a qualified buyer! Don't miss the chance to make it yours - schedule your tour today!
